I see — the `StringBuilder` doesn't have a `len()` method. I used `this.builder.len()` in the stringify code but it doesn't exist. I need to remove that check or use a different approach.

Let me look at how I'm using `this.builder.len()`:

```zig
// Add blank line before section (if there was previous content)
if (had_top_level or this.builder.len() > 0) {
    this.builder.append(.lchar, '\n');
}
